THIRD-PARTY API NOTICE

This software uses the following third-party APIs and data sources:

1. AniLibria public REST API (https://anilibria.top/api/v1/)
   Used to retrieve anime stream URLs.

2. AniList GraphQL API (https://graphql.anilist.co)
   Used to retrieve canonical anime titles by AniList ID.

3. Fribb anime-lists (https://github.com/Fribb/anime-lists)
   Used to map IMDB IDs to AniList, MAL, and AniDB IDs.

This project is an independent, unofficial addon and is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or sponsored by AniLibria, AniList, Fribb, or any of their
operators. All anime content, stream data, and related media accessed through
these APIs remain the property of their respective copyright holders. The
author of this software makes no claim of ownership over any third-party
content or data delivered via these APIs.

Use of each API is subject to its respective terms of service.
